---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Manifest and schema reference"
  description="Reference for the live llm-index.json manifest, the published JSON Schema, and the site's machine-facing entry points."
  eyebrow="Reference"
>
  <p>
    This page is a reference companion to the site's README.llm vNext example
    implementation.
  </p>

  <h2>Canonical artifacts</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><a href="/README.llm">`/README.llm`</a></li>
    <li><a href="/.well-known/llm-index.json">`/.well-known/llm-index.json`</a></li>
    <li>
      <a href="/schemas/readme-llm-vnext/manifest-0.1.schema.json">
        `/schemas/readme-llm-vnext/manifest-0.1.schema.json`
      </a>
    </li>
  </ul>

  <h2>What each artifact does</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>`README.llm` is the base machine entry point.</li>
    <li>`llm-index.json` is the retrieval manifest.</li>
    <li>The schema file defines the manifest structure.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>When to use this page</h2>
  <p>
    Use this page when you need an exact route, field name, or canonical schema
    URL. Use the how-to or tutorial sections when you need workflow guidance
    instead of factual lookup.
  </p>
</BaseLayout>
